			<title>[속보] 이 대통령, 여가부 장관 후보자에 원민경 변호사 지명</title>
			<description>&lt;p style="text-align: center; "&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="cheditor-caption-wrapper" style="text-align: center;"&gt;   &lt;figure class="cheditor-caption" style="background-color: #f0f0f0; max-width: 600px; margin: 0px auto; display: inline-block; width: 600px;"&gt;      &lt;img src="https://image.lawtimes.co.kr/thumb/180/210495.jpg" alt="34536.jpg" /&gt;      &lt;figcaption class="cheditor-caption-text" style="margin: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6em;"&gt;원민경 변호사&lt;/figcaption&gt;   &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;</description>
